'''Kells''' was the floating capital city of the planet [[Serob 6]]. Only 1% of the population was made up of the indigenous [[Sorki]]s, who preferred to dwell underwater; the rest consisted primarily of [[Human/Legends|Humans]] and other offworlders. These offworlders included masses of tourists, the local [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] governor and his staff, and an Imperial garrison.

During the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], the city was bombarded by a [[Droid/Legends|droid]]-manned fleet sent by the [[Artificial intelligence/Legends|AI]]. The Imperial Governor ordered the citizens to evacuate the city and seek refuge in underwater abysses.

